{"tid":805921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做地產代理都要有尊嚴","createTime":"2018-09-04T08:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T14:33:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d774c5d89f7bd820c205895c7b4f58b211e5178","tid":805921,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180904/58643462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180904%2F58643462&d=4LxgvR7ehd5k%2F1H1t1yFw8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=aa146ad3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180904%2F58643462&h=d613dfa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180904/58643462</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180904/large/1536048990_0f83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180904%2Flarge%2F1536048990_0f83.jpg&h=ec683df9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓花街霸惹人詬病，也影響行業形象，但公道一點說，不少街霸都辛勞地付出了努力的，日曬雨淋「水裡水裡去！」不是褒獎他們，而是有出力的人不應該被太貶低，個別樓花街霸的困擾問題只是源於指揮他們的管理層，攔截途人、馬路截車、違規的水票、甚至反悔承諾了客戶的回佣，不少也是在企業行為及人為「漏洞」下產生！<br />\n<br />\n近期，在樓花佣金回贈給客戶的反悔個案日益嚴重及趨向普及，地產代理監管局難免會多提示消費者，如此一來，行業的形象當然不會好了，作為代理，客戶要求我們提供佣金回贈當然是一個遺憾及損失，但是損失更大都不及因背信棄義而令行業蒙羞及令代理業不受信任，這損失的不單只是生意，而且是尊嚴了！<br />\n<br />\n消費者高抬貴手，對於付出真心努力的Sales，希望你們不要以減佣相待，但對於地產代理的佣金承諾，其實的確是需要在事前白紙黑字寫清楚的，個別常犯例的大型代理行，除了假盤外，更加應在樓花回贈上確保一諾千金！若個別大型地產代理都失信於公眾的時候，損失的不單只是消費者，而是將青春及家人生計也投身在地產代理行業的大部份從業員呢！<br />\n<br />\n最新代理公佈的持牌人數是39,591個，平均差不多6個人左右才有一宗成交，這比例其實是我經營的祥益地產百萬年薪人士的比例，為何我們細公司開單比例會不同？給員工合理的分享才是企業應有的責任啊！<br />\n<br />\n汪敦敬"},{"pid":"c23e5a53e6120fd9a395844f622be00858886921","tid":805921,"uid":36296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"總結：汪汪"},{"pid":"f06b51c0fa4c90f0191ea6354c37cdad192eeba3","tid":805921,"uid":30777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:01:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"bd7c53c19afbbc444b775910ff58dedf6c07b960","tid":805921,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"買一手樓必須回佣8成<br />\n買二手樓唔好比佣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c0fc4ee92f2d56c0da21f07c2d29e7324c6b9b","tid":805921,"uid":30777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd7c53c19afbbc444b775910ff58dedf6c07b960","tid":805921,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"買一手樓必須回佣8成<br />\n買二手樓唔好比佣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"死全家"},{"pid":"7dbf7d38f4e7c35ef31b4ab8ae416ebdedd5e002","tid":805921,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"龍市都做唔到生意，食屎啦"},{"pid":"e2e2ed47bea339acfdde37e4eba6a81312d4832d","tid":805921,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35c0fc4ee92f2d56c0da21f07c2d29e7324c6b9b","tid":805921,"uid":30777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd7c53c19afbbc444b775910ff58dedf6c07b960","tid":805921,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"買一手樓必須回佣8成<br />\n買二手樓唔好比佣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"死全家"},"cit